Events
.entry-header
Seadrift Sports Bar and Grill
Welcome to our Seadrift Events
Mondays and Thursdays there is free pool All Day!
Karaoke is held Sundays and Thursday from 9 p.m – 1 a.m
We offer Taco Tuesday every Tuesday here at Seadrift
Fridays are for Fish at Seadrift so we offer Fried Fish N Chips $12.95
We will help celebrate any party! Just call and ask for a manager!
We Have ALL NFL and College Football Games
.entry-content
